Ok, this thread isn't meant to be rude. Just...questioning...
I'm posting to question why Miss Silabsoft is AWSOME. Silab has been a member of staff for OVER 9000 years, but why? Silab has developed some great stuff beyond other programmers here, and is very intelligent and many people like her, but to be honest, she's not that great at coding jabas but awesome at playing flash flash revolution with her left hand. She often trolls and doesn't really ever do any actual moderating. Anyway, I'm looking to cause a community ruckus but failed :(
Post away.
